32300:Armas Silenciosas
32400:Armas Silenciosas
32500:armas silenciosas
32600:Devices designed to implement mind control on a global scale. They allow for the automation of society and the enslavement of all humanity except for the few Elite.[linebreak][linebreak]Based on the top secret document <i>S</i><i>i</i><i>l</i><i>e</i><i>n</i><i>t</i> <i>W</i><i>e</i><i>a</i><i>p</i><i>o</i><i>n</i><i>s</i> <i>f</i><i>o</i><i>r</i> <i>Q</i><i>u</i><i>i</i><i>e</i><i>t</i> <i>W</i><i>a</i><i>r</i><i>s</i> discovered in the United States.
