34800:Iglesia Cósmica de la Luz Divina
34900:Iglesia Cósmica de la Luz Divina
35000:iglesia cósmica de la luz divina
35100:(Fictional) A newly founded religion.[linebreak][linebreak]Inaugurated in 1930, their public estimate places their number of followers at around five million, but the actual number is thought to be closer to two million.[linebreak][linebreak]Its members are characterized by their ardent, forceful proselytization, which often causes repeated trouble for anyone involved.[linebreak][linebreak]Kuramochi Yuudai, the second generational founder, possesses absolute charisma, and in return, his followers offer absolute reverence.
35200:Nombre
