69200:Nombre
69300:Comité de los 300
69400:Comité de los 300
69500:comité de los 300
69600:A secret organization shrouded in mystery, rumored to manipulate the world from behind the scenes. Composed of only 300 members, they are known as the “Unseen Rulers.”[linebreak][linebreak]Their subordinates include the royalty of numerous nations, intelligence agencies, and large enterprises—with a focus on banking. They are all mere puppets of the 300, as are any other secret societies that often appear in conspiracy theories.[linebreak][linebreak]It is said that almost the entire world is bent to their will, whether it be companies, police, research institutes, etc.[linebreak][linebreak]However, their existence is only a rumor.[linebreak][linebreak]The Committee of 300's ultimate goal is theorized to be the construction of the so-called “New World Order” under the “Worldwide Human Domestication Project.” Outside of the few Elite, one billion humans will be left behind while all others are slaughtered. Those billion that survive will remain as slaves subject to the Rulers' administration.
69700:Nombre
